   for(i = 63; i >= 32; --i) {
```

## Resources

- RFC 8032 (Ed25519): https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8032#section-8.4
  - > Ed25519 and Ed448 signatures are not malleable due to the verification check that decoded S is smaller than l


